snippet: Top-ranked Novak Djokovic and No. 3 Andy Murray won their final group matches at the ATP finals in London, sending both into Sunday’s semifinals.
abstract: Novak Djokovic and Andy Murray win their final group matches at ATP finals tennis tournament, advancing into semifinals.
